headline: Joe Binz Appointed to Paycom’s Board of Directors
summary: OKLAHOMA CITY, December 12, 2024--Paycom Software, Inc. (NYSE: PAYC) ("Paycom"), a leading provider of comprehensive, cloud-based human capital management software, today announced the appointment of Joe Binz to Paycom’s board of directors, effective Dec. 10, 2024.
